A vintage 1970s-style illustration of a cozy living room scene featuring a glowing orange retro bubble-shaped computer monitor sitting sadly on a desk with a wilting flower beside it, while across the room a sleek modern flat-screen display and a tiny silver cube computer sit on an entertainment center, bathed in warm golden light from a nearby window. Two children sit cross-legged on a shag carpet between the old and new technology, looking back and forth between them with curious expressions. The color palette features harvest gold, avocado green, and burnt orange tones typical of mid-century domestic scenes, with subtle wood paneling on the walls and a lava lamp glowing softly in the corner.
